In [108]:
outliers=[]
def detect_outliers(lc):
    threshold=3
    mean=np.mean(lc)
    std=np.std(lc)
    
    for i in lc:
        z_score=(i-mean)/std
        if np.abs(z_score) > threshold:
            outliers.append(i)
    return outliers

outliers=[]
def detect_outliers(lc):
    threshold=3
    mean=np.mean(lc)
    std=np.std(lc)
    
    for i in lc:
        z_score=(i-mean)/std
        if np.abs(z_score) > threshold:
            outliers.append(i)
    return outliers
